後<br />\n我老母走咗去contact個師傅<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚柒<br />\n成廿歲人仲要老母幫<br />\n搞到好似小學雞喺學校有咩事<br />\n要老母見老師咁<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係要鬧我老母<br />\n但佢咁樣做令我好想搵窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 我到依家都未contact個師傅<br />\n好柒 唔撚知點面對佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:27:29.000Z","msg":"同佢玩車震叫佢寫你合格算數啦<br />\n你都係唔岩揸車"},{"pid":"506b5101a2cee58c647024242c2534d03bd79c04","tid":2317643,"uid":87172,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"屌你心情差就可以亂尻咁黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年先有個傻西剷左上行人路，撞低左幾個放學既細佬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14ecd42ba1c2a372e480a51f56c03f070be7eea","tid":2317643,"uid":377949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c09231fd23db24949afda2b68ed1d6797136326","tid":2317643,"uid":101732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:32:20.000Z","msg":"求下你唔好害人 quit啦"},{"pid":"c3f3fff31974505199f839596ab81b4248fbf32d","tid":2317643,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:32:25.000Z","msg":"如果連呢d 壓力都頂唔到，點揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2057a16397db2121eddec769c4beb3285c3e6d","tid":2317643,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:39:49.000Z","msg":"依個世界仲有巴士，小巴，的士，地鐵可以坐，唔洗絕望，最緊要唔好再掂軚盤得喇。"},{"pid":"3afe2f53f5734e4db9525c11adabaaefcfaf3588","tid":2317643,"uid":246704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><del>前日學車<br />\n嗰排心情唔太